name: scabrous uniparous
description:
Essentially my most difficult and complex moving images yet, I was going so hard on the NFT front working sometimes 15 or more hours a day mostly out of pure excitement of joy at the novelty of it all I almost burned myself out.
I was really fatigued and suffering all the worst because I hadnt made any new music in almost 2 months. So I took a break from it all, Twitter and the whole scene. I was able to do so and not be fixated on losing ground or making a shill post. It was nice and so this is what I got is something that is 10% the quality of my previous animations! enjoy.
